name: S. K. Prawns
overview:
Established in the year 2004, “S. K. Prawns & Agro Hindustan Ltd.”, are one of the prestigious firm engaged in trading and supplying uncontaminated Seafood.

Products & Services: Under the offered range, we provide Tiger Prawn, White Prawn, Black Prawn, Pompret Fish, Black Pompret Fish, Surmai Fish, Sea Crab, Tuna Fish, Rawas Fish, Barracuda Fish, Bombay Duck, Ghol Fish, Cat Fish, Butter Fish, Hilsa Fish, Tilapia Fish, Pearl Spot, Rohu Fish, Sea Lobster, Deep Sea Lobster, Rock Lobster, Dried Shrimp, Squid Whole beside these we also provide Commodity Trading & Agricultural Product.

Our Vision: “To Enrich the State of Maharashtra by Developing Innovative Aqua & Agri Products and in Diversified Areas by offering Superior Customer Services to Serve the People”.

Promoters & Management: The promoters are a team of professionals headed by Shri. Sanjay K. Patil, Chairman & Managing Director gives excellent support.

Our Vendors: For trading and supplying of Seafood & dealing in Agro Commodities, we have associated ourselves with the prestigious vendors of the industry.

Integrating Marketing Network: An integrated marketing network which includes the Cold Storage companies for the processing of the fisheries required for the supply to the local markets & exports for international market.
